**Distance & Time:** 19.3 miles, approximately **34 minutes** from central New York to JFK Airport. The route takes you via the Brooklyn Bridge, Brooklyn-Queens Expressway, Long Island Expressway, Grand Central Parkway, and Van Wyck Expressway.

## Current Time in Tokyo
**11:30 PM JST (Japan Standard Time)** on April 6, 2026
Tokyo is 13 hours ahead of Eastern Daylight Time (EDT).

## Weather in Tokyo
- **Temperature:** 58.2°F (approximately 14.6°C)
- **Wind Speed:** 5.3 mph (light winds)
- **Conditions:** Clear/Partly cloudy

